## Color Usage Guide

| Element                 | Token to use              | Hex                      |
| ----------------------- | ------------------------- | ------------------------ |
| Page background         | `--color-bg-primary`      | `#001439`                |
| Section alternate bg    | `--color-bg-secondary`    | `#001d52`                |
| Card background         | `--color-bg-card`         | `#002060`                |
| Primary button bg       | `--color-accent`          | `#2A8CD5`                |
| Primary button hover    | `--color-accent-hover`    | `#1e6fab`                |
| Links                   | `--color-accent`          | `#2A8CD5`                |
| Section headings        | `--color-highlight`       | `#9FCCFF`                |
| Body text               | `--color-text-primary`    | `#ffffff`                |
| Captions / labels       | `--color-text-secondary`  | `#9FCCFF`                |
| Borders                 | `--color-border`          | `rgba(42,140,213,0.25)`  |
| Focused borders         | `--color-border-strong`   | `#2A8CD5`                |
| Overlays / modals       | `--color-bg-overlay`      | `rgba(0,20,57,0.85)`     |
| Subtle tint backgrounds | `--color-highlight-muted` | `rgba(159,204,255,0.15)` |

