## Component Styling Rules

### Accept a `className` prop on every reusable component

```jsx
export default function Button({
  children,
  variant = "primary",
  className,
  ...props
}) {
  return (
    <button
      className={cn(
        "base-classes-here",
        variantClasses[variant],
        className, // ← always last so consumer can override
      )}
      {...props}
    >
      {children}
    </button>
  );
}
```

### Use `next/image` — never `<img>`

```jsx
import Image from 'next/image'

// ✅
<Image
  src="/images/products/transformer.jpg"
  alt="Smart Transformer X200"
  width={600}
  height={400}
  className="rounded-lg object-cover"
/>

// ❌
<img src="/images/products/transformer.jpg" alt="..." />
```

